Question: Are both the appliance that looks rectangular and the appliance to the right of the stove made of stainless steel?

Reference Answer: yes

Image path: ./sampled_GQA/n278312.jpg

Program:

```
BOX0=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='stove')
IMAGE0=CROP_RIGHTOF(image=IMAGE,box=BOX0)
BOX1=LOC(image=IMAGE0,object='appliance')
ANSWER0=VQA(image=IMAGE0,question='What color is the {appliance}?')
ANSWER1=EVAL(expr="'yes' if {ANSWER0} =='stainless steel' else 'no'")
BOX2=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='rectangular appliance')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=IMAGE,question='What color is the {rectangular appliance}?')
ANSWER3=EVAL(expr="'yes' if {ANSWER2} =='stainless steel' else 'no'")
ANSWER4=EVAL(expr="'yes' if {ANSWER1} == 'yes' and {ANSWER3} == 'yes' else 'no'")
FINAL_RESULT=RESULT(var=ANSWER4)
```
